VYHY DBUr-YHVH 'aLY L'aMUr.
BN-'aDM MH-YHYH 'yTSh-HGPhN MKL-'yTSh HZMVUrH 'aShUr HYH B'yTShY HY'yUr.
HYQCh MMNV 'yTSh L'yShVTh LML'aKH 'aM-YQChV MMNV YThD LThLVTh 'yLYV KL-KLY.
HNH L'aSh NThN L'aKLH 'aTh ShNY QTShVThYV 'aKLH H'aSh VThVKV NChUr HYTShLCh LML'aKH.
HNH BHYVThV ThMYM L'a Y'yShH LML'aKH 'aPh KY-'aSh 'aKLThHV VYChUr VN'yShH 'yVD LML'aKH.
LKN KH 'aMUr 'aDNY YHVH K'aShUr 'yTSh-HGPhN B'yTSh HY'yUr 'aShUr-NThThYV L'aSh L'aKLH KN NThThY 'aTh-YShBY YUrVShLM.
VNThThY 'aTh-PhNY BHM MH'aSh YTSh'aV VH'aSh Th'aKLM VYD'yThM KY-'aNY YHVH BShVMY 'aTh-PhNY BHM.
VNThThY 'aTh-H'aUrTSh ShMMH Y'yN M'yLV M'yL N'aM 'aDNY YHVH.
